1
00:00:06,039 --> 00:00:08,906
Good evening, sir. How was your day?
晚上好，先生。今天过的怎么样

2
00:00:08,975 --> 00:00:11,068
Being a lawyer stinks, Geoffrey.
当律师真是糟糕透了，Geoffrey

3
00:00:11,144 --> 00:00:12,611
No matter how good a job you do...
不管你的工作做得多么出色

4
00:00:12,679 --> 00:00:15,341
your clients still compare you
to Harry Hamlin.
你的委托人还是拿你
和Harry Hamlin（电影演员）比

5
00:00:16,349 --> 00:00:19,375
Yes. The resemblance is quite striking.
是的，你们相似点确实很多。

6
00:00:49,282 --> 00:00:51,910
Come on, baby. Get on the soul train.
来，宝贝。快来跳 soul train（一种舞蹈）

7
00:00:55,722 --> 00:00:59,021
l love this kind of dancing,
it makes you feel so young.
我很喜欢这类的舞蹈
让你感觉很年轻

8
00:00:59,859 --> 00:01:03,920
<i>Doesn't that goIden oIdie</i>
<i>take you way back?</i>
<i>这首经典名曲</i>
<i>有没有让你感觉回到了过去?</i>

9
00:01:05,331 --> 00:01:07,265
<i>That was</i> Papa's Got a Brand New Bag...
这首是<爸爸得到了一个新包包>

10
00:01:07,333 --> 00:01:11,064
<i>recorded 25 Iong years ago</i>
<i>by James Brown...</i>
是由James Brown在25年前录制的

11
00:01:11,137 --> 00:01:13,367
<i>the Granddaddy of SouI.</i>
老爷爷的灵魂

12
00:01:14,641 --> 00:01:17,974
<i>We'II be right back</i>
<i>after this message from GeritoI.</i>
广告之后
马上回来

13
00:01:19,712 --> 00:01:22,510
And the Fresh Prince
drives down the court.
新鲜王子带球冲到了前场

14
00:01:22,582 --> 00:01:26,143
He stops, he pops, and it's.... Yes!
瞄准，投篮....进了，太好了

15
00:01:26,619 --> 00:01:27,711
No.
一点也不好

16
00:01:28,621 --> 00:01:31,590
Will, don't play inside.
You might break something.
Will，不要家里面玩
你可能会打坏东西

17
00:01:31,658 --> 00:01:33,888
Or something might break you.
或者什么东西打坏你

18
00:01:33,960 --> 00:01:36,793
l'm sorry. You don't have a hoop outside.
我很抱歉。你们家外面没有篮筐

19
00:01:36,863 --> 00:01:40,094
And Jazz is getting tired of standing
on the second-floor balcony...
Jazz已经厌倦了站在二楼阳台上

20
00:01:40,166 --> 00:01:41,758
holding a pool skimmer.
端着一个破篮筐

21
00:01:42,068 --> 00:01:44,935
Come on, Prince, man.
l know a playground in my neighborhood.
走吧，哥们
我知道我邻居家有个球场

22
00:01:45,004 --> 00:01:46,596
'Course we can only play half-court.
但是我们只能打半场的

23
00:01:46,673 --> 00:01:49,471
They use the other end
to sell stolen appliances.
他们用另外半场
去卖那些偷来的小东西

24
00:01:50,343 --> 00:01:51,742
Dope. Let's go.
碉堡了。走起

25
00:01:51,911 --> 00:01:54,004
Hold on. We don't want you playing there.
等下。我们不希望你们在那里玩

26
00:01:54,080 --> 00:01:58,141
There's a perfectly good basketball court
at the school, where Carlton is practicing.
学校里有一个很完美的篮球场
Carlton就在那边练习

27
00:01:58,218 --> 00:02:00,482
Carlton's on the basketball team?
那货还会打篮球？

28
00:02:01,754 --> 00:02:03,278
How do they do?
他们打的怎么样

29
00:02:03,556 --> 00:02:07,993
They try hard, but to tell you the truth,
they haven't won a game so far.
他们很努力，但是说实话
他们到现在为止还没赢过

30
00:02:08,194 --> 00:02:11,891
Aunt Viv, don't you think
if we went down to watch them practice...
VIv小姨，你不觉得我们
去看他们训练

31
00:02:11,965 --> 00:02:14,661
Carlton would be a little embarrassed?
Carlton会有点小尴尬吗

32
00:02:15,335 --> 00:02:16,825
-Let's go.
-Let's go.
-走起
-走起

33
00:03:26,739 --> 00:03:28,104
All right.
好吧

34
00:03:30,009 --> 00:03:31,374
Good try!
做的很好

35
00:03:47,860 --> 00:03:49,885
Man, these guys need help.
哥们，这些人需要挽救

36
00:03:50,063 --> 00:03:52,224
Help? They need a telethon.
挽救？他们应该上慈善节目去娱乐大众

37
00:03:55,068 --> 00:03:56,501
He threw that ball to me.
那个球是传给我的

38
00:03:56,569 --> 00:03:59,231
l'm on the other team.
l'm supposed to try and get it.
我是另外一个队的
我本就该努力断球

39
00:03:59,305 --> 00:04:03,332
-You don't have to be rude about it.
-You two, make up right now.
-你没必要抢的那么粗鲁
-你们俩，赶紧和解。

40
00:04:06,446 --> 00:04:09,313
All right, men. Another brilliant warm-up.
好极了 又一次完美的热身

41
00:04:10,550 --> 00:04:14,008
Frankly, l think there's been
way too much emphasis over the years...
坦白说，这些年我已经用很多种
方式去强调

42
00:04:14,087 --> 00:04:17,113
on putting the ball
actually through the hoop.
把球投进篮框

43
00:04:17,323 --> 00:04:19,655
So let's practice some passing.
所以让我们练习下传球吧

44
00:04:20,827 --> 00:04:23,762
-Coach Smiley, may l have a minute?
-Sure.
-Smiley教练，能说句话不
-当然

45
00:04:24,864 --> 00:04:26,957
All right, men, take five.
先这样。小休一下

46
00:04:27,433 --> 00:04:29,333
Headmaster Thorvald, good afternoon.
Thorvard校长，下午好

47
00:04:29,402 --> 00:04:32,200
This is Barry O'Donnell.
He's a distinguished alumnus...
这个是 Barry O'Donnell
他是一名杰出校友

48
00:04:32,272 --> 00:04:35,298
and l'm encouraging him to donate money
for a new gymnasium.
我正在和他讨论为
新的健身房捐钱的事情

49
00:04:35,375 --> 00:04:38,640
Coach. What do you think
the team's prospects are this year?
教练。你认为今年球队的的目标
是什么

50
00:04:38,711 --> 00:04:39,905
For what?
什么目标

51
00:04:41,314 --> 00:04:42,747
For winning.
赢球的目标

52
00:04:43,783 --> 00:04:45,182
Excuse me.
不好意思

53
00:04:46,286 --> 00:04:49,619
What about those two?
You've been holding out on me.
那两个怎么样
你一直瞒着我

54
00:05:01,768 --> 00:05:04,100
Now those are players.
l'd like to meet them.
我很愿意见见
这些球员们

55
00:05:04,170 --> 00:05:05,535
Gentlemen.
先生们

56
00:05:06,339 --> 00:05:07,636
Not you.
不是你们

57
00:05:09,275 --> 00:05:12,608
You two, come on over.
l want you to meet somebody.
你们俩过来一下
我想让你们见个人

58
00:05:13,646 --> 00:05:16,774
Mr. Thorvald,
straight up, about that fire alarm:
Mr. Thorvald,
实话实说，那个报警铃

59
00:05:16,849 --> 00:05:18,680
l don't know who pulled it.
我也不知道谁拉的

60
00:05:19,585 --> 00:05:20,745
Forget about it.
旧事莫要重提

61
00:05:20,820 --> 00:05:23,812
l'd like you to meet two
of Bel-Air Academy's newest recruits.
为你介绍一下，这是贝莱尔学院
的最新成员

62
00:05:23,890 --> 00:05:27,348
This is Will Smith and.... Your name is....
这是Will Smith，你的名字是？

63
00:05:27,660 --> 00:05:29,093
Jazz, man.
Jazz，哥

64
00:05:29,195 --> 00:05:31,163
Of course, Mr. Jazzman.
哦对，Jazz哥先生

65
00:05:32,565 --> 00:05:35,227
Will, where have you been hiding yourself?
Will，你以前跑哪里去了

66
00:05:35,301 --> 00:05:37,235
What do you mean? During gym class?
什么意思？上体育课的时候？

67
00:05:37,303 --> 00:05:41,433
No. l just wondered, how'd you two men
like to join the school team?
不是。我刚刚在想
你们俩觉得加入校队怎么样

68
00:05:41,708 --> 00:05:44,176
Man, l ain't even in this school.
哥们，我根本不是这个学校的

69
00:05:44,477 --> 00:05:47,344
l'm willing to look past that if you are.
如果你加入的话我愿意接受

70
00:05:48,247 --> 00:05:51,216
Coach, he can't be on the team
if he's not in school here.
教练，如果他不在这个学校上学
是不能进入校队的

71
00:05:51,284 --> 00:05:53,411
Okay. How about you, Will?
Okay。你呢，Will？

72
00:05:53,820 --> 00:05:55,788
l was just trying to find
somewhere to play.
我就是想找个地方打篮球

73
00:05:55,855 --> 00:05:59,086
You join this team,
you can play here anytime you want.
你加入校队
什么时候想打都可以

74
00:05:59,292 --> 00:06:03,319
-No, l don't think so.
-lt'll look good on a college application.
-不，我还得考虑考虑
-这对申请大学有好处

75
00:06:03,429 --> 00:06:04,794
l don't know, Coach.
我还是很犹豫，教练

76
00:06:04,864 --> 00:06:07,298
All right. l'll give you my car.
再退一步。我把车借给你

77
00:06:09,635 --> 00:06:11,000
Okay, this is gonna be fun.
Okay，这会很好玩

78
00:06:11,070 --> 00:06:13,698
The coach asked me to go through
the playbook with you.
教练让我和你讨论下
战术

79
00:06:13,773 --> 00:06:17,072
Your team doesn't need a playbook.
They need a prayer book.
战术什么对这个队不管用吧
你们需要一本祈祷书

80
00:06:18,378 --> 00:06:20,107
Now, pay attention.
现在，注意听讲

81
00:06:20,213 --> 00:06:21,874
This is you...
这是你

82
00:06:22,682 --> 00:06:24,616
and this is me.
这是我

83
00:06:26,152 --> 00:06:29,644
Carlton, you got it wrong already.
lt's more like this.
Carlton，你大错特错了
应该这样画

84
00:06:30,456 --> 00:06:31,980
This is me.
这是我

85
00:06:33,860 --> 00:06:35,691
And this is you.
这是你

86
00:06:38,331 --> 00:06:39,491
Fair enough.
真公平

87
00:06:40,199 --> 00:06:42,531
This is my brain...
这是我的大脑

88
00:06:44,404 --> 00:06:46,338
and this is your brain.
这是你的大脑

89
00:06:48,641 --> 00:06:51,007
This is my handsome face.
这是哥那张帅气到家的脸

90
00:06:51,077 --> 00:06:54,240
And this is your ugly
little Frankenstein face.
这是你那张丑如little Frankenstein（丑陋无比的怪物）的脸

91
00:06:55,148 --> 00:06:57,207
-Give me that chalk.
-Come on, man, beat it.
-把粉笔给我
-来啊，想要就来抢

92
00:06:57,283 --> 00:06:59,376
-Give it.
-Ashley!
-给我
-Ashley！

93
00:06:59,886 --> 00:07:02,980
Here, Ashley,
finally there's an adult in the room.
给我吧，Ashley
这个屋子了总算是有个成熟的人了

94
00:07:05,191 --> 00:07:07,887
Guys, l'm trying to study.
What are you doing?
你们这些家伙，我在努力学习呢
你们干吗呢？

95
00:07:07,960 --> 00:07:10,793
-Keep away from Carlton.
-Over here.
-别让Carlton抢到粉笔
-这！这！这！

96
00:07:13,533 --> 00:07:15,000
Children, please!
小孩们，拜托

97
00:07:15,334 --> 00:07:17,495
What if your parents witnessed
this horseplay?
如果让你们父母目睹了这种恶作剧可不好

98
00:07:17,570 --> 00:07:20,266
-Give me that chalk immediately.
-Keep it away from Carlton!
-快把粉笔传给我！
-别让Carlton抢到！

99
00:07:20,339 --> 00:07:22,170
Keep away from Carlton and Geoffrey.
游戏规则变一下，别让
Carlton和Geoffrey抢到！

100
00:07:22,241 --> 00:07:25,267
You've met your match, Master William.
William少爷，这可是你自找的

101
00:07:27,780 --> 00:07:29,873
Geoffrey, get off me, man.
Geoffrey，快放开我

102
00:07:31,350 --> 00:07:32,647
Geoffrey?
Geoffrey？

103
00:07:33,853 --> 00:07:36,117
May l get you something, sir?
需要我为您做些什么吗，先生？

104
00:07:38,925 --> 00:07:40,483
No, thank you.
不了，谢谢

105
00:07:41,427 --> 00:07:44,453
Will, how many times
do l have to tell you...
Will，我告诉过你多少次了

106
00:07:44,530 --> 00:07:46,122
that this is our living room?
这是咱们的客厅

107
00:07:46,199 --> 00:07:50,192
How'd you like it if l went into your room
and started throwing chalk around?
如果我到你屋里去扔粉笔
你会怎么想

108
00:07:50,269 --> 00:07:51,964
l'd be devastated.
我会和你一起扔

109
00:08:00,012 --> 00:08:01,138
Out.
滚

110
00:08:05,284 --> 00:08:06,876
-Why did you do that?
-What?
-你为这么什么做？
-什么？

111
00:08:06,953 --> 00:08:09,285
You singled Will out.
They were all goofing around.
你把Will赶出去了
他们只是随便玩玩

112
00:08:09,355 --> 00:08:11,721
He was the mastermind. Trust me.
他绝对是主谋。相信我

113
00:08:11,858 --> 00:08:14,053
l just wish you'd be nicer to Will.
我只是希望你对Will好一点

114
00:08:14,126 --> 00:08:17,493
He joined the basketball team
and you haven't said a word about it.
他加入了篮球队
你却只字未提

115
00:08:17,563 --> 00:08:20,896
-Give him some credit.
-All right. l see your point.
-多给他赞扬和信任
-好吧，我懂你意思了

116
00:08:20,967 --> 00:08:25,427
Besides, l think it's a great opportunity
for you two to find some common ground.
此外，我认为这是你们俩找到
共同点的好机会

117
00:08:25,505 --> 00:08:28,565
After all, you were kind of
a star athlete in college.
毕竟你是学校的体育之星

118
00:08:28,641 --> 00:08:30,302
''Kind of a star athlete''?
“体育之星?”

119
00:08:30,376 --> 00:08:32,901
All right. You were a football god.
好吧，你是足球上帝

120
00:08:34,046 --> 00:08:36,207
Okay. Who knows,
it might do him some good.
就这样吧，谁知道呢
可能这样会对他好一点

121
00:08:36,282 --> 00:08:39,183
Nothing like a little organized sport
to straighten a guy out.
没什么有比一项运动
更能让他改邪归正的了

122
00:08:39,252 --> 00:08:41,982
Yes. lt did wonders for Pete Rose.
对，对Pete Rose（棒球运动员）来说是个奇迹

123
00:08:48,528 --> 00:08:52,692
Hilary, l appreciate you coming tonight.
l know you're not a big sports fan.
Hilary，我非常感谢你今天能来
我知道你并不太喜欢运动类的

124
00:08:52,865 --> 00:08:55,891
Mother, please,
it's Will's first game with the team.
妈呀，拜托。
这是Will的第一场比赛

125
00:08:55,968 --> 00:08:57,162
l'm proud of him.
我太为他自豪了

126
00:08:57,236 --> 00:09:00,467
lf l didn't show up to support him,
what kind of cousin would l be?
如果我连着都不支持他，
我算是哪门子表姐呢？

127
00:09:00,540 --> 00:09:02,940
lt'll be three hours well spent.
这将会是三个小时的视觉盛宴

128
00:09:03,175 --> 00:09:04,767
Three hours?
三个小时？

129
00:09:59,165 --> 00:10:02,601
Five, four, three, two, one!
5，4，3，2，1！

130
00:10:09,475 --> 00:10:11,466
l'm going to Disneyland!
我要去迪斯尼乐园了

131
00:10:16,282 --> 00:10:18,045
You did all right!
你今晚太棒了

132
00:10:33,299 --> 00:10:35,767
All right, men, good game on Friday.
棒极了。周五的比赛打得不错

133
00:10:35,835 --> 00:10:37,735
But we can do even better this week.
但是这周我们可以做的更好

134
00:10:37,803 --> 00:10:40,738
-So let's go over some plays.
-Sorry l'm late, Coach!
让我们重温下战术
对不起 教练 我迟到了

135
00:10:40,806 --> 00:10:42,569
Sorry isn't good enough, Cartwell.
Cartwell 光道歉是不够的

136
00:10:42,642 --> 00:10:46,373
-l was under the assumption--我有有原因的
-You made an assumption.你认为你有原因的

137
00:10:48,414 --> 00:10:52,009
Don't make an assumption...让我告诉你原因

138
00:10:52,351 --> 00:10:54,683
because you will be an ass...
因为你是一个傻逼

139
00:10:54,754 --> 00:10:57,245
and the ump will shun you.
连裁判都无视你

140
00:10:59,258 --> 00:11:02,284
Cartwell, after practice,
you give me 10 laps around the school.
Cartwell 训练结束后 你给我绕学校跑十圈

141
00:11:02,361 --> 00:11:03,487
Yes, Coach.
好的 教练

142
00:11:04,130 --> 00:11:06,098
Now let's take a look at this play.
现在 我们一起看下战术

143
00:11:06,165 --> 00:11:09,430
What's up? lt's my squad.
你们好吗 我的篮球队

144
00:11:11,103 --> 00:11:13,230
Sorry l'm late, Coach.
教练 对不起 我迟到了

145
00:11:13,305 --> 00:11:15,205
Don't worry about it, Smith.
没关系 Smith

146
00:11:15,274 --> 00:11:18,141
You just take it easy.
Save that energy for the game.
你只需要放轻松，为比赛节省能量

147
00:11:18,210 --> 00:11:20,178
But l was late, and l have to run 10 laps.
但是我迟到了，却要跑十圈

148
00:11:20,246 --> 00:11:22,043
Twenty laps. Now, shut up.
二十圈  闭嘴

149
00:11:24,350 --> 00:11:27,376
First play. Guard inbounds to the center.
第一种战术 后卫发边线球给中锋

150
00:11:27,453 --> 00:11:30,752
Center moves down court, fakes right,
passes to the forward.
中锋带球过半场 站好位 传球给前锋

151
00:11:30,823 --> 00:11:31,915
What does he do?
他该怎么做

152
00:11:31,991 --> 00:11:33,652
-Passes to Will?
-Bingo.
传给威尔 
答对了

153
00:11:34,794 --> 00:11:38,389
Second play. Jump ball.
Ball is tipped to the center.
第二中战术 跳球
把球拨给中锋

154
00:11:38,464 --> 00:11:40,762
Center shuttles to the guard,
back to the center...
中锋传给后卫，然后后卫再回传给中锋

155
00:11:40,833 --> 00:11:42,858
who hits to the forward
and over to baseline.
在传给前锋 在给到45°底线

156
00:11:42,935 --> 00:11:44,493
-What does he do?
-Passes to Will.
下一步他该怎么做
传给威尔

157
00:11:44,570 --> 00:11:45,696
Yes!
答对了

158
00:11:47,139 --> 00:11:49,573
Okay. Number three.
好了，第三种

159
00:11:49,775 --> 00:11:51,208
Forward inbounds from here...
前锋从这边发球

160
00:11:51,277 --> 00:11:54,041
bounce pass to the guard,
