309
00:22:07,292 --> 00:22:10,318
You started coming to games
when Will joined the team.
Will进了校队之后你才去
看比赛的

310
00:22:10,395 --> 00:22:14,388
-l wanted to support him.
-You wouldn't come when it was just me.
-我想支持他
-但是只有我的时候你没有支持

311
00:22:16,702 --> 00:22:19,068
l'd like to come to everything you do.
我很愿意为你去做任何事

312
00:22:19,137 --> 00:22:23,130
l always come to your tennis games,
to your debate matches...
你的每次网球比赛辩论会

313
00:22:23,208 --> 00:22:25,540
your glee club concerts.
你的翻唱团演唱会

314
00:22:25,610 --> 00:22:28,374
Frankly, keeping up
with your extracurricular activities...
和你去那些课外班 坦白说

315
00:22:28,447 --> 00:22:30,415
is a 24-hour-a-day job.
就是个24小时的活

316
00:22:31,249 --> 00:22:34,116
Did l mention
l was elected editor of the yearbook?
我说过我被选中成为年刊的编辑了吗？

317
00:22:35,220 --> 00:22:37,381
l didn't mean to slight you.
我没有想轻视你

318
00:22:37,622 --> 00:22:39,681
But l can't slight Will, either.
但是我也不能轻视Will

319
00:22:39,791 --> 00:22:42,259
His mother is 3,000 miles away.
他的妈妈在3000英里之外地方

320
00:22:42,327 --> 00:22:45,387
He needs a cheering section
as much as you do.
他也需要和你一样多的支持

321
00:22:45,464 --> 00:22:46,931
Maybe more.
甚至更多

322
00:22:49,568 --> 00:22:53,163
-l'm gonna head up. Good night, son.
-Good night, Dad.
-我明天还得早起。晚安，儿子
-晚安，爸爸

323
00:22:56,375 --> 00:22:57,603
Will.
威尔

324
00:22:58,710 --> 00:22:59,904
Yeah?
什么事

325
00:23:01,213 --> 00:23:02,339
Here.
给你


